|z|=1
|z|=1
|z|\leq 1
\sqrt{\frac{7}{2}}\leq |1+z|+|1-z+z^2|\leq 3\sqrt{\frac{7}{6}}
z=-\sqrt{\frac34} + \frac i2
|z|=1
|1+z|+|1-z+z^2|=3.2497>3\sqrt{\frac76}=3.2404
z=\frac12 + i\sqrt{\frac34}
|z|=1
|1+z|+|1-z+z^2|=1.7321<\sqrt{\frac72}=1.8708
z=\cos 2t+i\sin 2t,
|1+z|=|1+\cos 2t+i\sin 2t|=|2\cos^2t+i2\sin t\cos t|=|2\cos t||\cos t+i\sin t|=|2\cos t|
|1-z+z^2|=|1-(\cos 2t+i\sin 2t)+(\cos 2t+i\sin 2t)^2
=|1-(\cos 2t+i\sin 2t)+(\cos 4t+i\sin 4t)|
=|2\cos^22t-\cos 2t+i(2\sin2t\cos2t-\sin2t)|
=|(2\cos2t-1)(\cos 2t+i\sin2t)|=|(2\cos2t-1)||(\cos 2t+i\sin2t)|
=|(2\cos2t-1)|=|4\cos^2t-3|
|1+z|+|1-z+z^2|=2|\cos t|+|4\cos^2t-3|
|\cos t|= \cos t
\cos t\ge 0
-\cos t
|4\cos^2t-3|=-(4\cos^2t-3)
\cos^2t\le\frac34
-\frac{\sqrt3}2\le \cos t \le \frac{\sqrt3}2,
=4\cos^2t-3
\cos t\le-\frac{\sqrt3}2, |1+z|+|1-z+z^2|=-2\cos t+4\cos^2t-3
-\frac{\sqrt3}2< \cos t <0, |1+z|+|1-z+z^2|=-2\cos t-(4\cos^2t-3)
0\le \cos t \le \frac{\sqrt3}2, |1+z|+|1-z+z^2|=2\cos t-(4\cos^2t-3)
\cos t > \frac{\sqrt3}2 , |1+z|+|1-z+z^2|=2\cos t+(4\cos^2t-3)
\cos^2t\ge\frac34, -\cos t\ge \frac{\sqrt3}2\implies  |1+z|+|1-z+z^2|\ge 4\cdot\frac34+2\cdot\frac{\sqrt3}2-3={\sqrt3}
